    <briefdescription>
<para>Header for responses from embedded controller to host. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Represent the over-the-wire header in LE format for host command responses. This represent version 3 of the host command header. Responses are always sent from embedded controller to host. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
